ThinkPad Fan Control Extension
==============================

A GNOME Shell extension that provides safe, slider-based control over 
ThinkPad fan speeds with comprehensive safety features.

IMPORTANT SAFETY NOTICE:
This software controls hardware thermal management. While designed with 
safety features, users must understand the risks involved. Always monitor 
temperatures and use responsibly. The authors are not liable for hardware 
damage resulting from misuse.

Contact: https://github.com/NoXei/Fan-Control-Slider
